{"tid":331176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【上海冧樓】當局挖掘瓦礫 已確定4人死亡","createTime":"2017-07-22T02:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T07:16:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8b7d39e00d04add9025e209aa13a520d8a525d","tid":331176,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170722/large/1500682821_b227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170722%2Flarge%2F1500682821_b227.jpg&h=159f4d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170722/large/1500682819_71f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170722%2Flarge%2F1500682819_71f9.jpg&h=eb1773b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上海市嘉定區曹安公路華江路附近一棟正在拆卸的樓房，昨日下午近4時倒塌，壓倒旁邊的旅館。當局派人連夜在瓦礫堆中挖掘，至昨晚發現早前報稱失蹤的4人，其中有兩人證實不治，令到事故共造成4人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n當局使用重型機器在現場挖掘，第一批失蹤者在昨日傍晚6時許被發現，當中包括一男一女及一名小童，男女在送院途中已經死亡，男童則送到深切治療部搶救。現場消息稱有4人被埋，當局繼續發掘，至昨晚近10時許在瓦礫中發現失蹤者，其中兩人已經傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場救援、清理工作仍在進行。當局成立事故調查了組調查塌樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"e009399ded8a4729398b77b7b1d1b0fbc8108036","tid":331176,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32b528777a692e07297a3653ae441d1c99e21b04","tid":331176,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"無可能 支那唔會死人<br />\n如果有死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edfec7384b64f7b4e982f922b6a3cf1834843ad","tid":331176,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:29:01.000Z","msg":"支那人：你看我們拆房子多高效率"},{"pid":"0b94deb4c7e425d4f6d221d92805da04545bab